OL,3,CAyatollah says Iran will 'protect its
OL,4,Cnuclear capabilities' amid shaky
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FIran's supreme leader said the Islamic
OL,8,FRepublic will protect its "nuclear and
OL,9,Fmissile capabilities" as a national
OL,10,Fasset, as stalled US-Iran talks raised
OL,11,Fdoubts over the reopening of the
OL,12,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,14,FThe supreme leader is likely seeking
OL,15,Fto draw a hard line as US President
OL,16,FDonald Trump seeks a wider deal to
OL,17,Fcement the shaky ceasefire now holding
OL,18,Fin the war.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@UO]
