OL,3,CAyatollah says Iran will 'protect its
OL,4,Cnuclear capabilities' amid shaky
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FAyatollah Mojtaba Khamenei, speaking
OL,8,Fin a written statement read by a state
OL,9,Ftelevision anchor, struck a defiant
OL,10,Ftone, insisting the only place
OL,11,FAmericans belonged in the Persian Gulf
OL,12,Fis "at the bottom of its waters" and
OL,13,Fthat a "new chapter" was being written
OL,14,Fin the region's history.
OL,16,FHowever, his remarks come as Iran's
OL,17,Foil industry is being squeezed by a US
OL,18,FNavy blockade halting its oil tankers
OL,19,Ffrom getting out to sea.
OL,26,@tD@DOUuD@HOUuD@TO]
