OL,3,CAyatollah says Iran will 'protect its
OL,4,Cnuclear capabilities' amid shaky
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FMeanwhile, benchmark Brent crude for
OL,8,FJune delivery reached as much as $126
OL,9,Fa barrel in trading on Thursday.
OL,11,FAll this is putting additional
OL,12,Fpressure on the world's economy as
OL,13,FTrump likely weighs how to respond.
OL,15,F"By God's help and power, the bright
OL,16,Ffuture of the Persian Gulf region will
OL,17,Fbe a future without America, one
OL,18,Fserving the progress, comfort and
OL,19,Fprosperity of its people," Khamenei
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@ZO]
