OL,3,CAyatollah says Iran will 'protect its
OL,4,Cnuclear capabilities' amid shaky
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FHe was reportedly wounded in the 28
OL,8,FFebruary attack that killed his
OL,9,Ffather, the 86-year-old Supreme Leader
OL,10,FAyatollah Ali Khamenei.
OL,12,F"We and our neighbors across the
OL,13,Fwaters of the Persian Gulf and the
OL,14,F(Gulf) of Oman share a common destiny.
OL,15,FForeigners who come from thousands of
OL,16,Fkilometers away to act with greed and
OL,17,Fmalice there have no place in it `
OL,18,Fexcept at the bottom of its waters."
