OL,7,FHe referred to America as the "Great
OL,8,FSatan," a long hurled insult by
OL,9,FIranian leaders toward the US since
OL,10,Fthe 1979 Islamic Revolution.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FThe announcement comes after US
OL,18,FPresident Donald Trump posted an
OL,19,FAIgenerated image of himself holding
OL,20,Fa rifle on Wednesday, escalating his
OL,21,Fthreats towards Iran.
