OL,3,CAyatollah says Iran will 'protect its
OL,4,Cnuclear capabilities' amid shaky
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FPosting on his Truth Social, the
OL,8,Fpresident said the regime "can't get
OL,9,Fits act together" and doesn't know
OL,10,F"how to sign a non-nuclear deal".
OL,12,FAlongside the message, Trump posted an
OL,13,FAI-generated image of himself holding
OL,14,Fa weapon, with explosions in the
OL,15,Fbackground. The image included the
OL,16,Fstrapline "No more Mr Nice Guy!"
