OL,3,CAyatollah says Iran will 'protect its
OL,4,Cnuclear capabilities' amid shaky
OL,5,Cceasefire
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the price of Brent crude
OL,8,Foil briefly surged past $126 a barrel
OL,9,Fearly Thursday. Before the war began
OL,10,Fin late February, Brent crude was
OL,11,Ftrading around $70 per barrel.
OL,13,FThe US has continued its blockade of
OL,14,FIranian ports while the Strait of
OL,15,FHormuz is closed, pushing oil prices
OL,16,Fhigher.
OL,18,FReports on Wednesday night suggesting
OL,19,Fa possible escalation by Trump doused
OL,20,Fhopes for a quick end to the conflict.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
